WEBVTT

00:00:00.008 --> 00:00:03.488
Talk to Sahaja Yogis in Canberra, Australia, 20th March 1990

00:00:03.688 --> 00:00:07.735
Please, be seated, all of you.

00:00:13.732 --> 00:00:17.350
Please remove this one, if you can take it out.

00:00:17.550 --> 00:00:21.167
Please, be seated.

00:00:25.024 --> 00:00:27.000
We are all just the same, it’s one of the very important things

00:00:27.200 --> 00:00:33.199
we have to achieve, that we are all just
the same, there’s no difference between us.

00:00:33.399 --> 00:00:37.448
Apart from that, from our mundane life,

00:00:37.649 --> 00:00:41.463
it’s better that we stay in the ashram

00:00:41.663 --> 00:00:46.940
because children are looked after,
children become much more social,

00:00:47.140 --> 00:00:51.477
sensible and they understand meditation.

00:00:51.677 --> 00:00:56.272
And there’s a sort of discipline about it, meditation, people do meditation.

00:00:56.473 --> 00:01:00.654
In the house, they say: "Oh, I’m
alright on my own" and this and that.

00:01:00.854 --> 00:01:05.246
I know there have been problems, I agreed, there has been very bad leaders,

00:01:05.447 --> 00:01:11.097
and they were Australians, what
can I do? You are all Australians.

00:01:11.297 --> 00:01:13.920
I mean, I had to choose someone

00:01:14.120 --> 00:01:20.205
and the first who came to Sahaja Yoga, one after another.

00:01:20.405 --> 00:01:24.670
So they had to be appointed with. They turned out to be bad leaders,

00:01:24.871 --> 00:01:30.276
that’s, I don’t know, that’s the
lack of Australia I think. Alright.

00:01:30.557 --> 00:01:35.420
But doesn’t matter. You should not rebel, you should stay in the ashram,

00:01:35.621 --> 00:01:41.200
that’s very bad to rebel or to create
problems for collectivity, it’s sinful.

00:01:41.400 --> 00:01:45.411
And one has to pay for it. Those who create problems

00:01:45.611 --> 00:01:49.261
for collectivity are already paying through their noses,

00:01:49.461 --> 00:01:52.776
I know people, they develop, well, I don’t mean it at all,

00:01:52.976 --> 00:01:56.946
I don’t want it, they are feeling so frightened,

00:01:57.146 --> 00:01:59.977
that I’ve known people who’ve got cancers,

00:02:00.177 --> 00:02:04.320
have got heart attacks, have got horrible diseases.

00:02:04.520 --> 00:02:08.328
So, it’s very dangerous to do all these things, to get out of ashrams,

00:02:08.528 --> 00:02:12.894
form their own groups and work out that way, it’s very dangerous,

00:02:13.095 --> 00:02:19.284
it’s going against God, absolutely,
it’s like cutting God’s hands and feet.

00:02:19.484 --> 00:02:22.893
Nobody should try that.

00:02:23.093 --> 00:02:25.597
If you have any problem with the leaders, you can directly write to Me,

00:02:25.797 --> 00:02:28.860
I’ve been telling everybody. Why don’t you write to Me?

00:02:29.060 --> 00:02:31.407
They’ll write about everything, "my hair are falling,

00:02:31.607 --> 00:02:34.962
my nose is becoming smaller".

00:02:35.162 --> 00:02:37.835
Alls sorts of nonsense, twelve pages, they’ll write.

00:02:38.035 --> 00:02:40.120
But they never write what’s wrong with you

00:02:40.320 --> 00:02:44.705
and what’s wrong with the leader.

00:02:45.314 --> 00:02:47.677
And it’s very surprising, not one person wrote to Me

00:02:47.877 --> 00:02:52.581
till I discovered Myself. Everything I discovered Myself.

00:02:52.781 --> 00:02:56.284
Nobody wrote to Me anything about them. Then they move schools,

00:02:56.484 --> 00:03:00.830
they sell things, nobody tells Me anything about it.

00:03:01.030 --> 00:03:04.200
I was surprised when the school was moved from there to Sydney,

00:03:04.400 --> 00:03:08.161
without asking Me, without asking Me, they give,

00:03:08.361 --> 00:03:10.825
bought this Barwood, they bought that,

00:03:11.025 --> 00:03:14.208
gave up that place in Queue [unsure].

00:03:14.408 --> 00:03:19.743
I never knew! No one writes to Me!

00:03:19.943 --> 00:03:22.532
I mean, I have direct relationship with you.

00:03:22.732 --> 00:03:25.443
Of course, one has to have somebody, one person,

00:03:25.643 --> 00:03:31.588
to whom to contact, isn’t it? After all, I can’t write at all of them.

00:03:32.562 --> 00:03:37.620
But if you find anything wrong in the contact, you must inform it.

00:03:37.821 --> 00:03:40.744
But without ashrams, I don’t think you can be Sahaja Yogis,

00:03:40.944 --> 00:03:44.572
by any chance. By any chance, take it from Me.

00:03:44.772 --> 00:03:49.109
You cannot be Sahaja Yogis and you cannot be protected either,

00:03:49.310 --> 00:03:54.096
not at all. Today, maybe, if some people have gained some fame,

00:03:54.296 --> 00:03:58.471
some money, something, that’s not going to help you.

00:03:58.671 --> 00:04:04.185
Modern times are going to be terrible.

00:04:06.333 --> 00:04:09.248
It’s very wrong to do such things.

00:04:09.448 --> 00:04:14.378
You don’t know you are playing with fire.

00:04:15.808 --> 00:04:20.957
I already told you in Sahaja Yoga there
are two forces, centripetal and centrifuge.

00:04:21.157 --> 00:04:26.033
So according to the centripetal force, you are attracted in the centre.

00:04:26.233 --> 00:04:30.252
But centrifuge, you are thrown at a time jet.

00:04:30.452 --> 00:04:34.062
But when you get out of the control of God’s regime,

00:04:34.262 --> 00:04:39.655
then you fall into the trap. Anything can happen to you.

00:04:39.856 --> 00:04:47.100
I know of somebody who was just trying to be funny about Sahaja Yoga,

00:04:47.300 --> 00:04:53.017
he got into extreme and died
very suddenly. I was so chocked.

00:04:53.218 --> 00:04:56.560
The reports came that he’s started talking against Sahaja Yoga,

00:04:56.760 --> 00:05:00.385
he wanted to get out of Sahaja Yoga, he wanted to take some people

00:05:00.585 --> 00:05:03.814
and made a group and things like that. It’s very dangerous.

00:05:04.014 --> 00:05:07.586
Not for you but for your children and for the progeny of the whole lot.

00:05:07.786 --> 00:05:10.520
You are playing with fire, you must know this is a tremendous thing,

00:05:10.720 --> 00:05:14.896
we are doing now. It’s a tremendous task.

00:05:15.096 --> 00:05:21.615
It’s a very great work we are doing, emancipation of the whole humanity.

00:05:21.815 --> 00:05:24.441
And you can’t take liberties with it like this.

00:05:24.641 --> 00:05:28.722
Of course, there are a lot of blessings and advantages.

00:05:28.922 --> 00:05:31.993
But that doesn’t mean that we have the right to exploit it,

00:05:32.193 --> 00:05:36.313
by any chance. So please, immediately try to find some ashram,

00:05:36.513 --> 00:05:39.335
I want to protect your children, protect you all.

00:05:39.535 --> 00:05:43.413
If you are not in the ashram, I don’t know what will happen.

00:05:43.613 --> 00:05:46.436
And I’m not responsible, I must tell you very frankly.

00:05:46.636 --> 00:05:50.310
Recently, you must have heard about Germany’s things that happened.

00:05:50.511 --> 00:05:56.519
In Germany, this Hugo, he is another
Australian. He got some bhoot in him,

00:05:56.720 --> 00:05:58.801
I don’t know what happened. He suddenly got up and said:

00:05:59.001 --> 00:06:01.817
"I can also do Sahaja Yoga, why not?"

00:06:02.017 --> 00:06:04.446
And he was thinking he can form a group.

00:06:04.646 --> 00:06:08.282
He had already sent away two, three people from Russia.

00:06:08.482 --> 00:06:12.304
There was one mister Thomas who was an old Sahaja Yogi, he was nice.

00:06:12.505 --> 00:06:15.284
So when Hugo went there, he said: "No, nothing doing, I had close the door,

00:06:15.485 --> 00:06:19.040
I don’t want to hear anything of this mother, I don’t want to hear anything about it.

00:06:19.240 --> 00:06:23.833
Just don’t tell me." So mister Hugo went to another Sahaja Yogi

00:06:24.033 --> 00:06:27.489
who was, I would say, half-baked one, must have been.

00:06:27.690 --> 00:06:30.590
So they said, "we’ll start another ashram, we’ll start everything,

00:06:30.790 --> 00:06:33.348
do that alright."

00:06:33.548 --> 00:06:36.608
And the wife was rather obedient and she listened to all the nonsense

00:06:36.808 --> 00:06:42.366
that he was talking. And can you
imagine? She got cancer and she died.

00:06:42.566 --> 00:06:46.631
She came at a, absolutely, galloping stage to Shuddy camp.

00:06:46.831 --> 00:06:50.123
She confessed all this to Me. And her husband is dead also now,

00:06:50.323 --> 00:06:54.401
a cancer [inaudible].

00:06:54.787 --> 00:07:00.998
Because now, you are no more in the realm of God, finished.

00:07:05.945 --> 00:07:09.191
There’s no other worry, except for this, to Me.

00:07:09.391 --> 00:07:12.772
Because if you are in Sahaja Yoga, you’ll be looked after, your jobs,

00:07:12.973 --> 00:07:16.462
your health, your children, and I’ve no worry at all,

00:07:16.662 --> 00:07:18.984
in every way, you’ll be provided for,

00:07:19.184 --> 00:07:23.289
because Sahaja Yoga is such a caring thing, it cares for you.

00:07:23.489 --> 00:07:28.037
But if you don’t care for your own Sahaja Yoga, you have to suffer,

00:07:28.237 --> 00:07:30.737
suffers in such a long way.

00:07:30.938 --> 00:07:33.999
Don’t support your wife or husband in this kind of a nonsense.

00:07:34.199 --> 00:07:36.492
If they do it, you say: "We are going to leave you, go to hell;

00:07:36.692 --> 00:07:39.109
we have nothing to do with you."

00:07:39.309 --> 00:07:43.273
I must warn you all because it’s now again, coming up in Australia,

00:07:43.473 --> 00:07:49.077
this kind of a dislocation. Now Steven
is there who, I must say, has a bad luck

00:07:49.277 --> 00:07:54.460
because he’s got all the bad things, it’s a bad government,

00:07:54.660 --> 00:07:58.187
leaves debts on the next one coming, like that,

00:07:58.387 --> 00:08:01.739
it’s all on him and he is quite lenient.

00:08:01.939 --> 00:08:05.903
He, he must have thought, "the others were very harsh,

00:08:06.103 --> 00:08:09.065
so I should be lenient." So he’s lenient.

00:08:09.265 --> 00:08:11.840
So people will start, you see, to put things away.

00:08:12.040 --> 00:08:15.229
But everybody has to be self-disciplined in Sahaja Yoga.

00:08:15.429 --> 00:08:19.228
You must have that much sense, and that much self-esteem,

00:08:19.428 --> 00:08:23.002
self control, to have self-discipline yourself.

00:08:23.202 --> 00:08:27.064
Because whatever is good for you, you have taken up such a big job now,

00:08:27.264 --> 00:08:33.622
it’s to emancipate the whole humanity.
It’s not talking, it’s just there.

00:08:33.822 --> 00:08:39.298
I’ve been telling everyone in Australia.

00:08:39.499 --> 00:08:43.237
I’m rather surprised how this idea is rolling up everywhere,

00:08:43.437 --> 00:08:46.803
that they should have separate houses. First I met with this idea further

00:08:47.003 --> 00:08:50.952
and I blasted it out. I said:"Nothing doing."

00:08:51.152 --> 00:08:57.680
I don’t know where you stay, what is your
area, where, how am I to protect you?

00:08:57.880 --> 00:09:02.292
It’s just ego.

00:09:03.417 --> 00:09:06.886
One Indian girl was telling Me she’s so happy in an ashram,

00:09:07.087 --> 00:09:11.575
because there are other people in the house,
you see, a burglar comes in, we are not worried

00:09:11.775 --> 00:09:16.872
because there are other people in the house.
"I feel so safe, the children are looked after,

00:09:17.072 --> 00:09:23.714
if you are going out they’ll say: "Alright,
we’ll look after your children you can go."

00:09:23.914 --> 00:09:28.180
And everything works out better. It’s much cheaper to live in an ashram,

00:09:28.380 --> 00:09:31.751
much less work, much less labour.

00:09:31.951 --> 00:09:36.147
And the real thing is the ascent part of it.

00:09:36.347 --> 00:09:39.303
It’s all ego, please face it, please face it.

00:09:39.503 --> 00:09:43.528
Ego and small mindedness, very small mindedness.

00:09:43.728 --> 00:09:45.988
You must have a proper vision of yourself, what you could be.

00:09:46.188 --> 00:09:50.020
You can be like the sky while you want to be like a ditch,

00:09:50.220 --> 00:09:54.749
what can you do?

00:09:56.819 --> 00:09:59.304
And our lifestyle is different, we have a close lifestyle,

00:09:59.504 --> 00:10:02.937
that’s why it’s more important. We are not like India.

00:10:03.137 --> 00:10:05.843
In India, you see, every body will just jostle with each other,

00:10:06.043 --> 00:10:08.927
they are going into that house, and that house, nothing is close,

00:10:09.127 --> 00:10:12.404
except for so called little bit sophisticated, westernized.

00:10:12.604 --> 00:10:15.138
Otherwise, they meet everyone, talk to everyone,

00:10:15.338 --> 00:10:20.640
everybody knows about everyone, everything.

00:10:21.922 --> 00:10:24.728
They keep a sort of big ashram, we can say.

00:10:24.942 --> 00:10:31.183
And there are certain rules and regulations
that they follow among themselves, no problem.

00:10:31.553 --> 00:10:34.725
But this individualism is not going to help us at all,

00:10:34.925 --> 00:10:38.421
not at all. It’s a collective happening, you know that.

00:10:38.621 --> 00:10:40.760
It’s like if My nail is cut and put somewhere,

00:10:40.960 --> 00:10:45.132
I’m not going to bother about it.

00:10:45.332 --> 00:10:49.350
It’s selfishness,

00:10:49.550 --> 00:10:53.404
absolutely. I must tell you frankly, I must tell you the truth

00:10:53.604 --> 00:10:57.121
because I’m your Mother, I’m not going to tell you lies.

00:10:57.321 --> 00:10:59.762
I’m not going to please you, because I’m not standing for elections

00:10:59.962 --> 00:11:06.204
or anything, I am what I am,; whether
you accept Me or not, I am what I am.

00:11:06.405 --> 00:11:09.238
But I’ve to tell you the truth.

00:11:09.439 --> 00:11:11.960
Or else, if you have a large house, you can have some more people there

00:11:12.160 --> 00:11:14.351
staying with you, you can form an ashram.

00:11:14.551 --> 00:11:18.068
But don’t have your own family with you, "my own children, my",

00:11:18.268 --> 00:11:23.572
once you go on "my, my" then I disappear.

00:11:31.351 --> 00:11:35.539
She’s trying to talk to Me.

00:11:36.336 --> 00:11:38.173
Hello.

00:11:38.373 --> 00:11:42.680
Because you laugh, now she’s self conscious.

00:12:00.057 --> 00:12:03.545
What do you want? Raise their Kundalini?

00:12:03.745 --> 00:12:07.321
What is your idea? You want to raise their Kundalini?

00:12:07.521 --> 00:12:13.435
Yes, here, she understands. Oh, that’s catching. She is saying this.

00:12:15.104 --> 00:12:19.026
Alright, this. Thank you very much.

00:12:19.227 --> 00:12:23.996
Oh, beautiful.

00:12:37.631 --> 00:12:45.240
A mint [sweet] with a hole, like Sahaja Yogis, a mint with a hole.

00:12:47.159 --> 00:12:52.783
Alright. So this is something serious, it should be understood seriously,

00:12:52.984 --> 00:12:56.348
not to be heard from one ear: "Oh, Mother says so this thing,

00:12:56.548 --> 00:13:02.579
nothing’s there." You must understand, it’s very important.

00:13:04.937 --> 00:13:07.934
And that they get cancer, come to Me: "Mother we’ve got cancer."

00:13:08.134 --> 00:13:11.535
"What were you doing?" "We were still staying separately." "Why?"

00:13:11.735 --> 00:13:16.300
"Why will you stay?"

00:13:30.186 --> 00:13:39.470
If they really got troubles from the head or from the called the leaders,

00:13:39.670 --> 00:13:42.392
you must let Me know.

00:13:42.592 --> 00:13:45.718
Well, this is as simple as anything. I’m your Mother,

00:13:45.918 --> 00:13:49.179
I’ve given you the second birth, why shouldn’t you write to Me?

00:13:49.379 --> 00:13:53.973
Everything well, what so ever.

00:13:55.115 --> 00:13:57.890
I’ll be always with you, whatever may happen

00:13:58.091 --> 00:14:01.857
and whosoever you may be. First, you have done some mistakes,

00:14:02.065 --> 00:14:04.429
it’s alright that I tell you, it’s dirty [inaudible],

00:14:04.629 --> 00:14:09.648
but otherwise you must tell Me everything. It’s very important.

00:14:09.848 --> 00:14:15.733
I’m not only you Guru, but I’m your Mother.

00:14:16.788 --> 00:14:22.880
Do you find anything wrong with Me that you don’t tell Me?

00:14:25.214 --> 00:14:28.232
If you write nonsensical things, twenty fours pages letter,

00:14:28.432 --> 00:14:34.534
still I’ll read. Though I know it’s nonsense, still I read it.

00:14:40.274 --> 00:14:46.447
So, I expect you to write to Me about yourself,

00:14:46.647 --> 00:14:49.760
about your children, anything wrong in the whole leadership,

00:14:49.960 --> 00:14:53.304
or anything like that, you must write to Me. Anything you are doing,

00:14:53.504 --> 00:14:55.750
you should write to Me, what you are doing about Sahaja Yoga,

00:14:55.950 --> 00:14:58.781
you should write to Me, because God will ask you:

00:14:58.981 --> 00:15:03.077
"What did you do for Sahaja Yoga?" Mother gave you Realization,

00:15:03.278 --> 00:15:06.466
She travelled all the way, everywhere She went, did this, did that.

00:15:06.666 --> 00:15:09.800
I mean, I’m, I’m, my life is such now

00:15:10.000 --> 00:15:14.085
that I’m neither living in My house nor in an ashram.

00:15:14.285 --> 00:15:20.483
I’m just in the air all the time. I live
more in the aeroplanes than in the houses.

00:15:20.683 --> 00:15:25.680
And we must also do something else, isn’t it?
We should work it out a little bit for Mother.

00:15:25.880 --> 00:15:28.809
"What are we doing here? How many places we have been?

00:15:29.009 --> 00:15:32.328
Where did we arrange the program?" Like that, you have to think.

00:15:32.528 --> 00:15:35.040
But if you are not collective, you’ll never think like this.

00:15:35.240 --> 00:15:38.380
Because your attention will be: "Now my house is there,

00:15:38.580 --> 00:15:41.667
this has to be paid, that has to be done and I have to get this."

00:15:41.867 --> 00:15:46.995
But if you’re in an ashram, you’ll think: "How we’ll spread Sahaja Yoga?"

00:15:47.195 --> 00:15:52.787
That will be the main topic on your head.

00:15:57.247 --> 00:16:02.745
Alright, so now, at the very beginning,
I didn’t want to say all these things,

00:16:02.945 --> 00:16:07.308
but I just felt that it is important, very important.

00:16:07.508 --> 00:16:12.349
So basically, that point is: all should sit down and think it over that

00:16:12.549 --> 00:16:16.357
"We have to have a place which is our own",

00:16:16.557 --> 00:16:19.560
may be on rent, doesn’t matter, you own your own, it’s better.

00:16:19.760 --> 00:16:22.966
"There’s that house that is good, this house is good,

00:16:23.166 --> 00:16:25.560
that house is good, that house is good", go on saying,

00:16:25.760 --> 00:16:29.740
that house is good, you like it, alright have it.

00:16:29.940 --> 00:16:33.714
Whichever house you’ll like. That’s how you’ll look after.

00:16:33.914 --> 00:16:38.324
But you must decide, you have to look after and find a house.

00:16:38.524 --> 00:16:41.738
I Myself was seeking one house for you.

00:16:41.938 --> 00:16:44.433
We will point out.

00:16:44.633 --> 00:16:47.246
See the vibrations and go ahead with it.

00:16:47.446 --> 00:16:51.551
We are not here, Sahaja Yoga is not for the people who are by the way.

00:16:51.751 --> 00:16:55.300
No. On the contrary, they become like the murmuring souls that

00:16:55.500 --> 00:16:59.339
Christ has described. He said: "Murmuring souls are the worst people".

00:16:59.539 --> 00:17:04.117
Those who are not there are alright,
because they will be destroyed in any case.

00:17:04.318 --> 00:17:09.337
But those who are half way, they’ll have a much worst time.

00:17:14.242 --> 00:17:17.572
All of you should combine and go through everything.

00:17:17.773 --> 00:17:22.393
And you must let Me know if there’s any problem, alright?

00:17:22.593 --> 00:17:26.633
So now for today, let us see and just try to find out, if possible,

00:17:26.833 --> 00:17:30.563
if there’s any house, when I’m here.

00:17:30.763 --> 00:17:35.341
I would love(?) in My house.

00:17:38.882 --> 00:17:41.560
Children always like company, they fell lonely

00:17:41.760 --> 00:17:45.049
if they are given some separate, they don’t like it.

00:17:45.249 --> 00:17:48.328
When they are with company they enjoy, they don’t like to live alone.

00:17:48.528 --> 00:17:52.160
"Then why should we? We are people who are Ganapatis,

00:17:52.360 --> 00:17:56.185
we are innocent people, why should we have all other things

00:17:56.385 --> 00:18:00.885
like the useless grown-ups have?"

00:18:01.573 --> 00:18:04.988
You ask children: as soon as they see each other, they’ll hug,

00:18:05.188 --> 00:18:08.058
they’ll kiss each other, they’ll talk to each other,

00:18:08.258 --> 00:18:10.806
they always want the company of the children.

00:18:11.006 --> 00:18:15.897
You can’t keep them separated.

00:18:17.849 --> 00:18:20.297
And then happiness will come, then joy will come,

00:18:20.497 --> 00:18:25.829
then security will come and mainly the growth. Alright?

00:18:26.029 --> 00:18:28.938
Now so may God bless you.

00:18:29.138 --> 00:18:34.394
Now you’d better go and look out for a house.

00:18:36.956 --> 00:18:39.362
I asked - Delhi people have built a house.

00:18:39.563 --> 00:18:42.160
There are also bureaucrats and stupid people there.

00:18:42.360 --> 00:18:45.809
And they built such a nice ashram there.

00:18:46.009 --> 00:18:48.360
So I said: "What about some people staying there?"

00:18:48.561 --> 00:18:51.354
Of course, they go very often, live very often and Indians are,

00:18:51.554 --> 00:18:54.315
there’s a rapport all the time, they contact each other,

00:18:54.515 --> 00:18:57.667
open house they have. So they said: "Mother you"-

00:18:57.867 --> 00:19:01.080
I said: "There are so many ashrams, and in how many ashrams,

00:19:01.280 --> 00:19:04.962
I’m going to live and what about you people living there?"

00:19:05.162 --> 00:19:09.597
So ashrams are built for Me only.

00:19:11.706 --> 00:19:16.720
That is so funny.

00:19:19.301 --> 00:19:22.234
So I will request you now to give up all these ideas,

00:19:22.434 --> 00:19:25.211
otherwise I’m not responsible for you at all.

00:19:25.411 --> 00:19:29.690
Not at all, I tell you, it’s impossible.

00:19:32.526 --> 00:19:35.720
And, if it was only one case or two cases, I would have said:

00:19:35.920 --> 00:19:38.703
"Alright, doesn’t matter, we’ll see." But it’s so common now that

00:19:38.904 --> 00:19:43.900
I’m frightened, absolutely frightened. I don’t want my children to be lost.

00:19:44.100 --> 00:19:47.712
They all have to be in one boat. Otherwise some are in the water,

00:19:47.912 --> 00:19:50.000
some are hanging to the boat and some are inside.

00:19:50.200 --> 00:19:52.509
I don’t like that kind of things. No mother would like,

00:19:52.709 --> 00:19:56.802
I don’t feel peaceful with you, I fell very nervous. Alright?

00:19:57.002 --> 00:20:01.440
So you understand My concern about you and I mean it,

00:20:01.640 --> 00:20:05.823
I really mean it serious.

00:20:06.023 --> 00:20:10.668
May God bless you.

00:20:15.098 --> 00:20:21.581
In any case, I’m working it out within Myself, and you also work it out.

00:20:22.709 --> 00:20:24.709
This is very nice (?).
